WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.120 --> 00:00:01.422
Hey, good morning family.

00:00:01.422 --> 00:00:03.839
I'm excited to be with you all again today.

00:00:04.319 --> 00:00:09.909
I've taken some time to pray and I've been seeking the Lord about 2024.

00:00:12.810 --> 00:00:26.138
I don't take this lightly, speaking to you all like this and telling you all what's coming and warning you about the Father's Heart and what's going on in the spirit realm.

00:00:27.613 --> 00:00:39.572
Like I said, I've just been taking some time seeking Him, getting into the Word more, and not allowing all the pressure of life to try to squash out the voice.

00:00:40.426 --> 00:00:43.103
This has been a trip for me.

00:00:43.103 --> 00:00:54.720
I just started this YouTube channel in March, and it's been like a fire hose the last couple of weeks with all the stuff coming—not necessarily always good.

00:00:59.616 --> 00:01:06.023
I just want to take some time; I have a hard word to give again.

00:01:09.030 --> 00:01:17.520
I'm going to say it like this: the Lord's called me to say the hard things, y'all, and it's not always easy being me.

00:01:18.130 --> 00:01:26.171
But I'm going to tell you exactly what's going on regardless of all this other crap you're hearing on the other platforms.

00:01:26.429 --> 00:01:29.719
That's what I'm going to tell you: it's pure crap.

00:01:29.719 --> 00:01:44.607
After sitting before the Father last night and getting the download that I got, I hope you all still stick around because I'm going to tell you the truth about what's coming, and you all need to hear it.

00:01:44.983 --> 00:01:46.488
So here it goes.

00:01:46.488 --> 00:01:58.007
I was praying before, just like I always do, and I felt the heaviness coming on me.

00:01:58.007 --> 00:02:11.691
It was very intense intercessory prayer, and all of a sudden, I know when the Lord's about to speak now because I feel it; it's like a bubble up inside of me prophetically.

00:02:12.120 --> 00:02:20.408
So I told my son, 'Get the recorder out right now because I don't want to forget anything He's going to talk about.

00:02:20.408 --> 00:02:25.149
' All of a sudden, the Word of the Lord came up to me and I saw a vision.

00:02:25.577 --> 00:02:28.800
I saw preachers standing behind the pulpits.

00:02:29.159 --> 00:02:36.818
Holy Spirit, I ask you to deliver it just the way you delivered it the first time.

00:02:36.818 --> 00:02:38.314
Thank you.

00:02:38.314 --> 00:02:53.776
I saw preachers standing behind the pulpit and they had oil—this smooth, oily-looking oil—all over their mouths and it was dripping from their lips.

00:02:54.394 --> 00:03:02.274
They had roaches and bugs crawling in and out of their mouths and laying upon their lips.

00:03:02.274 --> 00:03:11.704
Bugs were crawling in their teeth and in and out of their mouths and they would lay upon their lips as they would speak.

00:03:12.128 --> 00:03:30.578
They had a shrewdness in their eyes; their motives behind what they were preaching were all selfish gain, trying to appease the ear of the people.

00:03:30.578 --> 00:03:49.064
Then I saw ears on the people, and I could see their ears were just being pacified by all these whispers of the things that were happening in the spirit: 'Everything is going to be good; all things are going to work for your good for those that love the Lord.

00:03:49.064 --> 00:03:54.189
' They were speaking the Word, but they were not speaking what was on God's heart.

00:03:54.189 --> 00:03:59.840
They were speaking things, but they weren't speaking things to make you grow.

00:04:00.138 --> 00:04:11.820
I saw these bugs coming out of their teeth and out of their mouths, and I looked across the land of America.

00:04:12.360 --> 00:04:17.708
There were babies with diapers on all throughout the land.

00:04:17.708 --> 00:04:20.205
There was nobody with backbone.

00:04:20.205 --> 00:04:26.914
They were all like really lethargic babies that had diapers on—these Pampers.

00:04:27.331 --> 00:04:34.230
I saw, whenever you see soiled diapers, the smell that rises up like in cartoons.

00:04:37.959 --> 00:04:43.983
All the babies had soiled diapers on and there were flies buzzing around those babies.

00:04:44.434 --> 00:04:52.666
The babies were crying, 'Please, change my diaper!

00:04:52.666 --> 00:05:03.470
' There were literally thousands and thousands and thousands of babies full of dirty diapers, and the preachers were not teaching them.

00:05:03.741 --> 00:05:18.326
The Lord spoke to me and he said, 'Brandon, the preachers are not teaching the milk or the meat of the word to grow my children up into adult stature.

00:05:18.326 --> 00:05:25.946
' He said, 'Therefore, there is going to be a great shifting upon the land.

00:05:25.946 --> 00:05:34.719
' He said, 'They have raised their noses towards me with a stiff neck.

00:05:34.719 --> 00:05:37.876
' Their noses were pointed up towards God.

00:05:37.876 --> 00:05:41.250
I saw a pride that was upon the people.

00:05:41.615 --> 00:05:48.102
He said, 'There's a pride upon the people and they have a stench before me.

00:05:48.102 --> 00:05:50.228
Therefore, what is coming...

00:06:02.520 --> 00:06:02.980
there are prophecies going forth about a great revival, about a great harvest, about all these things, but judgment comes in the house of the Lord first.

00:06:02.980 --> 00:06:14.471
Therefore, there will be a great shifting take place and there will be what people call a great Ichabod come upon the land.

00:06:14.471 --> 00:06:21.370
' He said, 'I have told you this before, but there will be a great Ichabod come upon the land.

00:06:21.370 --> 00:06:29.109
' It would seem like it, but I will never leave you and I will never leave nor will I forsake you.

00:06:29.109 --> 00:06:36.160
But there will be a shifting, and he said a shaking is coming to the Body.

00:06:36.703 --> 00:06:50.069
I saw a sluice box, the kind that sifts dirt from the gold, and I saw this manure, dirt, and all this debris inside this box.

00:06:56.844 --> 00:06:59.120
He said, 'You have to shift the box.

00:06:59.120 --> 00:07:10.474
' He showed me Him sifting the box and shaking it so the gold rises to the top and the dirt was falling to the ground.

00:07:11.873 --> 00:07:14.600
But it comes through a great shaking.

00:07:14.600 --> 00:07:21.449
He said, 'You have to shake all the debris and all the stuff off so that the gold will rise.

00:07:21.449 --> 00:07:27.542
' Then he said, 'I want you to focus on the great sequoia tree out in California.

00:07:27.542 --> 00:07:29.377
' He said, 'I want you to focus.

00:07:29.377 --> 00:07:41.256
' He said, 'The seed does not produce until there is great fire upon it, and it will be released when there is fire upon it.

00:07:41.256 --> 00:07:46.952
' He said, 'You will be like the great sequoia tree that grows its roots down deep.

00:07:46.952 --> 00:07:56.680
' I saw a fire coming upon the land, but it was like a refiner's fire—not a physical fire, but a refiner's fire.

00:08:00.639 --> 00:08:13.950
I saw the refiner's fire burning upon the seed and all of a sudden, the ground from as far as the eye could see was completely charred, tested by fire.

00:08:14.420 --> 00:08:27.360
In this 'tested by fire,' then I saw new growth, new green grass growing because the weeds and all the stuff were burnt up.

00:08:27.811 --> 00:08:33.335
I saw green, new flowers, beautiful new things coming.

00:08:33.335 --> 00:08:43.840
I saw those sequoia plants being planted and growing up because of the fire and the testing that was coming upon the people.

00:08:45.000 --> 00:08:46.489
The Lord told me, he showed me...

00:08:49.452 --> 00:08:56.827
like I tell you all, I see calendars sometimes and he shows me things like in windows of time.

00:08:57.200 --> 00:08:59.945
I saw a time of testing coming.

00:08:59.945 --> 00:09:05.229
I saw times of hardship coming upon the people.

00:09:05.229 --> 00:09:15.280
I saw the glorious church rising in a window of time with great glory.

00:09:15.280 --> 00:09:26.371
I saw an outpouring of the spirit of God and healings and manifestations of the glory beyond anybody's comprehension.

00:09:26.371 --> 00:09:29.978
But he said the church is not ready for this.

00:09:29.978 --> 00:09:41.964
He said, 'There must be holiness and righteousness preached back in the pulpits to shake the people, to teach them how to stand on the meat of the word, not on the milk of the word.

00:09:41.964 --> 00:09:49.420
' There are too many babies and therefore there will be a great shaking coming.

00:09:49.800 --> 00:09:58.547
Like I said, then all of a sudden I saw people that he said, 'You call me Lord, Lord.

00:09:58.942 --> 00:10:00.524
You call me savior.

00:10:00.524 --> 00:10:02.253
You call me your friend.

00:10:02.253 --> 00:10:07.240
' He said, 'I do not know you, for your heart is far from me.

00:10:07.240 --> 00:10:17.891
' He said, 'Just like Peter that said he would never deny me, he denied me three times.

00:10:17.891 --> 00:10:34.390
' Therefore, there will be a lot of you that, just when pressure comes and these great trials come—as the shiftings and the refining fire comes on them—he said, 'You have called me Lord, Lord, but you will deny me three times just like Peter did.

00:10:34.390 --> 00:10:48.680
' He said there will be a great shifting in this and a great falling away for the ones that call me Lord, Lord, but never really truly made me Lord of their life and made me savior over them.

00:10:49.040 --> 00:10:59.906
Therefore, those who rise up out of that fire and that refining, he said they are the ones that will have boldness to walk before me in these end times.

00:10:59.906 --> 00:11:12.160
'Did I not say in my word,' he said, 'that in the end many will come to me saying, "Did I not prophesy in your name?

00:11:12.160 --> 00:11:14.972
Did I not lay hands on the sick in your name?

00:11:14.972 --> 00:11:18.560
Did I not cast out devils in your name?

00:11:18.560 --> 00:11:22.206
"' and he said, 'Depart from me, I never knew you.

00:11:22.206 --> 00:11:30.170
' Those scriptures are true and they are alive and they are going forth, and this will happen.

00:11:30.170 --> 00:11:31.584
Do you understand?

00:11:31.584 --> 00:11:38.260
Those were prophecies that God spoke before the beginning of time.

00:11:38.260 --> 00:11:46.339
Look at the words that are coming to pass: all men's hearts will fail them for fear for what's coming upon the earth.

00:11:46.339 --> 00:11:48.509
They will be lovers of themselves.

00:11:49.330 --> 00:11:55.616
It is coming upon the land even more—even a greater loving of self.

00:11:55.616 --> 00:11:57.332
They have itching ears.

00:11:57.332 --> 00:12:00.683
Their hearts are full of gall and evilness.

00:12:03.560 --> 00:12:09.093
But the Lord says he's bringing forth a refiner's fire, and many will say it is a great Ichabod.

00:12:10.849 --> 00:12:17.156
Many will say what's coming is a great Ichabod, but it is not an Ichabod; it is refining.

00:12:18.292 --> 00:12:32.560
Like I said, I'm not coming on here to give you an itching ear word today to tell you everything is always going to be good for some folks, but I'm going to tell you: if you're walking with the Lord right now, you'll lack nothing.

00:12:33.999 --> 00:12:51.376
Everything will always be okay with you if you are already walking with Him, if you're walking through that refiner's fire, if you're standing before Him righteous and listening to Him every day and praying and seeking His face daily and reading His word and having fellowship with Him.

00:12:52.199 --> 00:12:58.669
The Word said, 'I'll never see the righteous forsaken or his seed begging bread.

00:12:58.669 --> 00:13:00.411
' Think about what He's saying.

00:13:00.760 --> 00:13:02.760
Many of you say, 'Well, I'm righteous.

00:13:02.760 --> 00:13:06.669
' No, you're not; you're walking in compromise.

00:13:06.669 --> 00:13:13.011
I'm coming to tell you there's a lot of you that are babies, just like he told me, and the babies are upon the land.

00:13:13.388 --> 00:13:24.195
The preachers have been preaching you a smooth, oily, roach-filled word; they aren't teaching you how to stand.

00:13:24.195 --> 00:13:27.540
You come to this channel and I'm going to tell you: Jesus loves you.

00:13:28.604 --> 00:13:31.192
He loves you, but he wants you to grow up.

00:13:31.192 --> 00:13:37.360
He wants you to put your big boy pants on or big girl pants on and walk with him.

00:13:37.360 --> 00:13:39.595
Stop being these little babies.

00:13:39.595 --> 00:13:43.942
Get a spine; stand for what the word says.

00:13:43.942 --> 00:13:47.729
Repent, turn from your wicked ways.

00:13:55.646 --> 00:13:56.171
You've got to get your heart before Him.

00:13:56.171 --> 00:14:05.159
Turn—intercession starts to hit me again—you've got to repent and turn because Jesus is coming.

00:14:08.831 --> 00:14:10.960
You've got to get your heart right before him because Jesus is coming and you aren't ready.

00:14:10.960 --> 00:14:15.019
I'm going to try to tell you all: you've got to get righteous before him.

00:14:15.019 --> 00:14:17.206
