00:15:27.840 --> 00:15:39.810
I try to speak to the remnant, but I know I have a lot of babies on my channel and I'm trying to tell you it's time to get in the word; it's time to memorize that scripture.

00:15:39.810 --> 00:15:42.391
It's time to turn from your wicked ways.

00:15:46.059 --> 00:15:46.279
You know, a lot of people say, 'Turn or burn.

00:15:46.279 --> 00:15:47.982
' You need to turn, separate yourself.

00:15:50.867 --> 00:15:51.036
